1. https://www.mingw-w64.org/downloads/#mingw-builds접속

2. Mingw-builds Sourcforce 클릭 후 mingw64.exe 실행 후 설치

3. C:\Program Files\mingw-w64\x86_64-8.1.0-posix-seh-rt_v6-rev0 설치경로 확인

4. 고급시스템 설정 > 환경변수 > 사용자/시스템 변수 > path > 새로만들기 경로 추가

(C:\Program Files\mingw-w64\x86_64-8.1.0-posix-seh-rt_v6-rev0 + \bin ->C:\Program Files\mingw-w64\x86_64-8.1.0-posix-seh-rt_v6-rev0\bin)

5. anaconda prompt 관리자 권한으로 실행 

conda install mkl

conda install libpython

pip install theano

conda install -c conda-forge libpython mkl-service m2w64-toolchain numba python-graphviz scipy

(pip uninstall pymc3)

pip install pymc3
